high_descs: turn right and face the front of the desk
grab the wrist watch off of the desk
turn around and move over to the right side of the desk
place the wrist watch on the cabinet to the bottom right of the desk
move to the right side of the desk
grab a different wrist watch off the top of the desk there
move around to face the front of the desk
place the second wrist watch in the cabinet where you placed the other wrist watch

high_descs: Walk forward one step then turn right and walk to the table with a light on it.
Pick up the watch that's sitting under the light.
Position yourself so you are on the other side of the table so the black chair is to the left of you and you are facing the wall with the desk in front of you.
Put the watch on the left side of the shelf under the top of the table to the right of the chair.
Turn right and walk to the glass doors then turn left and walk to the wall then turn left.
Pick up the watch that's in front of you.
Walk back to where you placed the first watch.
Put the watch to the right of the other watch.
anns.task_desc: Place two watches on a shelf.

high_descs: Turn to your right and approach the desk.
Pick up a watch from the desk.
Turn around and walk to the other end of the desk
Place the watch inside the desk.
Walk to the right of the desk and face the end.
Pick up another watch from the desk.
Return to the front of the desk.
Place this watch next to the other one.
anns.task_desc: Move two watches to the inside of a desk.
